{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/springboot-jwt-tutorial1/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>인프런 강의(Spring Boot JWT Tutorial)를 수강하며, 내용들을 기록한 페이지입니다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>배우는 것</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Spring Boot를 이용한 JWT 인증, 인가 구현</li>\n<li>Spring Security 기초</li>\n<li>회원가입, 로그인, 권한로직</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"jwt-소개-jwtio-홈페이지\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#jwt-%EC%86%8C%EA%B0%9C-jwtio-%ED%99%88%ED%8E%98%EC%9D%B4%EC%A7%80\" aria-label=\"jwt 소개 jwtio 홈페이지 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>JWT 소개 (<a href=\"http://JWT.io\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">JWT.io</a> <a href=\"https://jwt.io\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">홈페이지</a>)</h1>\n<hr>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/88a3671ae2a14a75a78cab96fd2c59f8/9e9da/1-1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52.02702702702703%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Untitled\"\n        title=\"Untitled\"\n        src=\"/static/88a3671ae2a14a75a78cab96fd2c59f8/fcda8/1-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/88a3671ae2a14a75a78cab96fd2c59f8/12f09/1-1.png 148w,\n/static/88a3671ae2a14a75a78cab96fd2c59f8/e4a3f/1-1.png 295w,\n/static/88a3671ae2a14a75a78cab96fd2c59f8/fcda8/1-1.png 590w,\n/static/88a3671ae2a14a75a78cab96fd2c59f8/efc66/1-1.png 885w,\n/static/88a3671ae2a14a75a78cab96fd2c59f8/c83ae/1-1.png 1180w,\n/static/88a3671ae2a14a75a78cab96fd2c59f8/9e9da/1-1.png 2482w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>JWT 는 Json 객체를 사용하여 토큰 자체에 정보들을 저장하고 있는 Web Token 이라 할 수 있다.</p>\n<p>특히, JWT를 이용하는 방식은 헤비하지 않고 아주 간편하고 쉽게 적응할 수 있다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>JWT 는 Header, Payload, Signature  3개의 부분으로 구성되어 있다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Header : Signature 를 해싱하기 위한 알고리즘 정보들이 담김</li>\n<li>Payload :  서버와 클라이언트가 주고받는, 시스템에서 실제로 사용될 정보에 대한 내용들을 담고있다.</li>\n<li>Signature : 토큰의 유효성 검증을 위한 문자열</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>장점</p>\n<ul>\n<li>중앙의 인증서버, 데이터 스토어에 대한 의존성 없음, 수평확장에 유리</li>\n<li>Base64 URL Safe Encoding  > URL, Cookie, Header 모두 사용 가능</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>단점</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Payload 의 정보가 많아지면 네트워크 사용량 증가, 데이터 설계 고려 필요</li>\n<li>토큰이 클라이언트에 저장, 서버에서 클라이언트의 토큰을 조작할 수 없음</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"프로젝트-생성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"프로젝트 생성 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>프로젝트 생성</h2>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"1-스프링-이니셜라이저를-통한-프로젝트-생성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-%EC%8A%A4%ED%94%84%EB%A7%81-%EC%9D%B4%EB%8B%88%EC%85%9C%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B4%EC%A0%80%EB%A5%BC-%ED%86%B5%ED%95%9C-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"1 스프링 이니셜라이저를 통한 프로젝트 생성 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. 스프링 이니셜라이저를 통한 프로젝트 생성</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f2e9a8f00b9e3814d4c597a3e3ba37e2/5f78c/1-2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 78.37837837837837%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Untitled\"\n        title=\"Untitled\"\n        src=\"/static/f2e9a8f00b9e3814d4c597a3e3ba37e2/fcda8/1-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f2e9a8f00b9e3814d4c597a3e3ba37e2/12f09/1-2.png 148w,\n/static/f2e9a8f00b9e3814d4c597a3e3ba37e2/e4a3f/1-2.png 295w,\n/static/f2e9a8f00b9e3814d4c597a3e3ba37e2/fcda8/1-2.png 590w,\n/static/f2e9a8f00b9e3814d4c597a3e3ba37e2/efc66/1-2.png 885w,\n/static/f2e9a8f00b9e3814d4c597a3e3ba37e2/c83ae/1-2.png 1180w,\n/static/f2e9a8f00b9e3814d4c597a3e3ba37e2/5f78c/1-2.png 1606w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>프로젝트 메타데이터를 입력한다</li>\n<li>자바 버전은 8</li>\n<li>빌드 도구는 Gradle</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/754804375c9e5960dc03c6c1977898f3/ae28e/1-3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 78.37837837837837%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Untitled\"\n        title=\"Untitled\"\n        src=\"/static/754804375c9e5960dc03c6c1977898f3/fcda8/1-3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/754804375c9e5960dc03c6c1977898f3/12f09/1-3.png 148w,\n/static/754804375c9e5960dc03c6c1977898f3/e4a3f/1-3.png 295w,\n/static/754804375c9e5960dc03c6c1977898f3/fcda8/1-3.png 590w,\n/static/754804375c9e5960dc03c6c1977898f3/efc66/1-3.png 885w,\n/static/754804375c9e5960dc03c6c1977898f3/c83ae/1-3.png 1180w,\n/static/754804375c9e5960dc03c6c1977898f3/ae28e/1-3.png 1598w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>스프링 부트 버전은 2.6.2 (강좌는 2.4.1임)</li>\n<li>\n<p>추가한 의존성</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Lombok (편의성)</li>\n<li>Spring Web</li>\n<li>Spring Security</li>\n<li>h2 Database</li>\n<li>Spring Data JPA</li>\n<li>Validation</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8c7a6f9158b7a95d78c0fae9b946f2e9/aca16/1-5.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 57.432432432432435%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Untitled\"\n        title=\"Untitled\"\n        src=\"/static/8c7a6f9158b7a95d78c0fae9b946f2e9/fcda8/1-5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8c7a6f9158b7a95d78c0fae9b946f2e9/12f09/1-5.png 148w,\n/static/8c7a6f9158b7a95d78c0fae9b946f2e9/e4a3f/1-5.png 295w,\n/static/8c7a6f9158b7a95d78c0fae9b946f2e9/fcda8/1-5.png 590w,\n/static/8c7a6f9158b7a95d78c0fae9b946f2e9/efc66/1-5.png 885w,\n/static/8c7a6f9158b7a95d78c0fae9b946f2e9/c83ae/1-5.png 1180w,\n/static/8c7a6f9158b7a95d78c0fae9b946f2e9/aca16/1-5.png 3230w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>프로젝트가 생성된 모습</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/281457bc0d8de06e9154113c0c182475/99f37/1-4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 12.162162162162163%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('