to; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/529136b76721e5a1433bdedbe829eca8/33d1d/1-6.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 58.78378378378378%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Untitled\"\n        title=\"Untitled\"\n        src=\"/static/529136b76721e5a1433bdedbe829eca8/fcda8/1-6.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/529136b76721e5a1433bdedbe829eca8/12f09/1-6.png 148w,\n/static/529136b76721e5a1433bdedbe829eca8/e4a3f/1-6.png 295w,\n/static/529136b76721e5a1433bdedbe829eca8/fcda8/1-6.png 590w,\n/static/529136b76721e5a1433bdedbe829eca8/efc66/1-6.png 885w,\n/static/529136b76721e5a1433bdedbe829eca8/33d1d/1-6.png 1150w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>간단한 문자열(hello)을 리턴해주는 api를 만들고 테스트해보겠습니다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">RestController</code> : 컨트롤러를 JSON을 반환하는 컨트롤러로 만들어 줍니다.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">RequestMapping</code> : 요청에 대해 어떤 Controller가 처리할지를 맵핑하기 위한 어노테이션.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">GetMapping</code> : HTTP Method인 Get인 요청을 받을 수 있는 API를 만들어 준다.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">ResponseEntity&lt;&gt;</code> : 사용자의 HttpRequest에 대한 응답 데이터를 포함하는 클래스.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">ResponseEntity.ok()</code>: 정상적인 요청이면 메소드의 파라미터 내용을 반환한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>위 코드를 작성하고 애플리케이션을 실행하고 Postman을 통해서 해당 url로 요청을 보내겠습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/782385618d9b437d671ef95062473db3/6c86f/1-7.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 44.5945945945946%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Untitled\"\n        title=\"Untitled\"\n        src=\"/static/782385618d9b437d671ef95062473db3/fcda8/1-7.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/782385618d9b437d671ef95062473db3/12f09/1-7.png 148w,\n/static/782385618d9b437d671ef95062473db3/e4a3f/1-7.png 295w,\n/static/782385618d9b437d671ef95062473db3/fcda8/1-7.png 590w,\n/static/782385618d9b437d671ef95062473db3/efc66/1-7.png 885w,\n/static/782385618d9b437d671ef95062473db3/c83ae/1-7.png 1180w,\n/static/782385618d9b437d671ef95062473db3/6c86f/1-7.png 1720w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>요청을 보내면 401 HTTP 상태 코드가 반환된 것을 볼 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p>이를 해결하기 위한 Security 설정과, 기본적인 Data 설정을 하겠습니다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"reference\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#reference\" aria-label=\"reference permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Reference</h3>